/12/Screenshot-2023-12-20-at-15.18.51-694x183.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-20-at-15.18.51-1280x337.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-20-at-15.18.51-768x202.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-20-at-15.18.51-1536x404.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>值得一提的是，Ivacy VPN 本身容許 10 個裝置一起使用，因此與家人或朋友夾錢買的話就會是最抵用，而且一個收費終身有效的話，更不用擔心之後再次付款時加價之類的問題，想趁機會入手的話，記得用優惠特別連結（<a href="https://billing.ivacy.com/page/92307">按此連結</a>）然後輸入「Ivacy10」優惠碼來訂購啦！</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/22/ivacy-vpn-year-end-2023/life-tech/">Ivacy VPN 年末最後優惠　教你如何 54 美元買終身版</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
